{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882566279,"sessionID":"ses_28526aca8fferZlun7r4EHxBjU","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad97052001z694K6na947ILs","messageID":"msg_d7ad96598001XRgS03L5aHT0tz","sessionID":"ses_28526aca8fferZlun7r4EHxBjU","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_2d450e4c2ab54ccabba8f646","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/Makefile"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/Makefile</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Makefile for AgentCube Docker builds\n2: # Provides targets for building, pushing, and managing container images\n3: \n4: # Docker configuration\n5: DOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\n6: DOCKER_TAG ?= latest\n7: VERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty 2>/dev/null || echo \"dev\")\n8: COMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")\n9: \n10: # Image names\n11: WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\n12: ROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router\n13: PICOD_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod\n14: \n15: # Build all images\n16: .PHONY: docker-build-all\n17: docker-build-all: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-picod\n18: \t@echo \"✓ All images built successfully\"\n19: \n20: # Build Workload Manager image\n21: .PHONY: docker-build-workloadmanager\n22: docker-build-workloadmanager:\n23: \t@echo \"Building Workload Manager image...\"\n24: \tdocker build \\\n25: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile \\\n26: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n27: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n28: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n29: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n30: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) \\\n31: \t\t.\n32: \t@echo \"✓ Workload Manager image built: $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n33: \n34: # Build Router image\n35: .PHONY: docker-build-router\n36: docker-build-router:\n37: \t@echo \"Building Router image...\"\n38: \tdocker build \\\n39: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n40: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n41: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n42: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n43: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n44: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) \\\n45: \t\t.\n46: \t@echo \"✓ Router image built: $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n47: \n48: # Build Picod image\n49: .PHONY: docker-build-picod\n50: docker-build-picod:\n51: \t@echo \"Building Picod image...\"\n52: \tdocker build \\\n53: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod \\\n54: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n55: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n56: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n57: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n58: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(VERSION) \\\n59: \t\t.\n60: \t@echo \"✓ Picod image built: $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n61: \n62: # Push all images\n63: .PHONY: docker-push-all\n64: docker-push-all: docker-push-workloadmanager docker-push-router docker-push-picod\n65: \t@echo \"✓ All images pushed successfully\"\n66: \n67: # Push Workload Manager image\n68: .PHONY: docker-push-workloadmanager\n69: docker-push-workloadmanager:\n70: \t@echo \"Pushing Workload Manager image to $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)...\"\n71: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n72: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n73: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(VERSION)\n74: \n75: # Push Router image\n76: .PHONY: docker-push-router\n77: docker-push-router:\n78: \t@echo \"Pushing Router image to $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)...\"\n79: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n80: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n81: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(VERSION)\n82: \n83: # Push Picod image\n84: .PHONY: docker-push-picod\n85: docker-push-picod:\n86: \t@echo \"Pushing Picod image to $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)...\"\n87: \tdocker push $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n88: \tdocker push $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n89: \tdocker push $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(VERSION)\n90: \n91: # Load images to Kind cluster\n92: .PHONY: kind-load-all\n93: kind-load-all: kind-load-workloadmanager kind-load-router kind-load-picod\n94: \t@echo \"✓ All images loaded to Kind cluster\"\n95: \n96: .PHONY: kind-load-workloadmanager\n97: kind-load-workloadmanager:\n98: \tkind load docker-image $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n99: \n100: .PHONY: kind-load-router\n101: kind-load-router:\n102: \tkind load docker-image $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n103: \n104: .PHONY: kind-load-picod\n105: kind-load-picod:\n106: \tkind load docker-image $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n107: \n108: # Multi-architecture build (requires Docker Buildx)\n109: .PHONY: docker-buildx-all\n110: docker-buildx-all: docker-buildx-workloadmanager docker-buildx-router docker-buildx-picod\n111: \t@echo \"✓ All multi-arch images built successfully\"\n112: \n113: .PHONY: docker-buildx-workloadmanager\n114: docker-buildx-workloadmanager:\n115: \t@echo \"Building multi-arch Workload Manager image...\"\n116: \tdocker buildx build \\\n117: \t\t--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n118: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile \\\n119: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n120: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n121: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n122: \t\t--push \\\n123: \t\t.\n124: \n125: .PHONY: docker-buildx-router\n126: docker-buildx-router:\n127: \t@echo \"Building multi-arch Router image...\"\n128: \tdocker buildx build \\\n129: \t\t--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n130: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n131: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n132: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n133: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n134: \t\t--push \\\n135: \t\t.\n136: \n137: .PHONY: docker-buildx-picod\n138: docker-buildx-picod:\n139: \t@echo \"Building multi-arch Picod image...\"\n140: \tdocker buildx build \\\n141: \t\t--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n142: \t\t-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod \\\n143: \t\t--build-arg VERSION=$(VERSION) \\\n144: \t\t--build-arg COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n145: \t\t-t $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n146: \t\t--push \\\n147: \t\t.\n148: \n149: # Clean up local images\n150: .PHONY: docker-clean\n151: docker-clean:\n152: \t@echo \"Cleaning up local Docker images...\"\n153: \t-docker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n154: \t-docker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) 2>/dev/null || true\n155: \t-docker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) 2>/dev/null || true\n156: \t-docker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n157: \t-docker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) 2>/dev/null || true\n158: \t-docker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(VERSION) 2>/dev/null || true\n159: \t-docker rmi $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n160: \t-docker rmi $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) 2>/dev/null || true\n161: \t-docker rmi $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(VERSION) 2>/dev/null || true\n162: \t@echo \"✓ Cleanup complete\"\n163: \n164: # Validate images (size, security, configuration)\n165: .PHONY: docker-validate\n166: docker-validate: docker-validate-workloadmanager docker-validate-router docker-validate-picod\n167: \t@echo \"✓ All images validated successfully\"\n168: \n169: .PHONY: docker-validate-workloadmanager\n170: docker-validate-workloadmanager:\n171: \t@echo \"Validating Workload Manager image...\"\n172: \t@./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n173: \n174: .PHONY: docker-validate-router\n175: docker-validate-router:\n176: \t@echo \"Validating Router image...\"\n177: \t@./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n178: \n179: .PHONY: docker-validate-picod\n180: docker-validate-picod:\n181: \t@echo \"Validating Picod image...\"\n182: \t@./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n183: \n184: # Run all tests\n185: .PHONY: docker-test\n186: docker-test: docker-test-build docker-test-runtime\n187: \t@echo \"✓ All Docker tests passed\"\n188: \n189: .PHONY: docker-test-build\n190: docker-test-build:\n191: \t@echo \"Running build tests...\"\n192: \t@./deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh\n193: \n194: .PHONY: docker-test-runtime\n195: docker-test-runtime:\n196: \t@echo \"Running runtime tests...\"\n197: \t@./deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh\n198: \n199: # Help target\n200: .PHONY: help\n201: help:\n202: \t@echo \"AgentCube Docker Makefile\"\n203: \t@echo \"\"\n204: \t@echo \"Build targets:\"\n205: \t@echo \"  docker-build-all              - Build all three images\"\n206: \t@echo \"  docker-build-workloadmanager  - Build Workload Manager image\"\n207: \t@echo \"  docker-build-router           - Build Router image\"\n208: \t@echo \"  docker-build-picod            - Build Picod image\"\n209: \t@echo \"\"\n210: \t@echo \"Push targets:\"\n211: \t@echo \"  docker-push-all               - Push all images to registry\"\n212: \t@echo \"  docker-push-workloadmanager   - Push Workload Manager image\"\n213: \t@echo \"  docker-push-router            - Push Router image\"\n214: \t@echo \"  docker-push-picod             - Push Picod image\"\n215: \t@echo \"\"\n216: \t@echo \"Kind targets:\"\n217: \t@echo \"  kind-load-all                 - Load all images to Kind cluster\"\n218: \t@echo \"  kind-load-workloadmanager     - Load Workload Manager image\"\n219: \t@echo \"  kind-load-router              - Load Router image\"\n220: \t@echo \"  kind-load-picod               - Load Picod image\"\n221: \t@echo \"\"\n222: \t@echo \"Multi-arch targets:\"\n223: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-all             - Build multi-arch images (amd64, arm64)\"\n224: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-workloadmanager - Build multi-arch Workload Manager\"\n225: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-router          - Build multi-arch Router\"\n226: \t@echo \"  docker-buildx-picod           - Build multi-arch Picod\"\n227: \t@echo \"\"\n228: \t@echo \"Test & validate targets:\"\n229: \t@echo \"  docker-test                   - Run all Docker tests\"\n230: \t@echo \"  docker-validate               - Validate all images\"\n231: \t@echo \"  docker-clean                  - Clean up local images\"\n232: \t@echo \"\"\n233: \t@echo \"Variables:\"\n234: \t@echo \"  DOCKER_REGISTRY=$(DOCKER_REGISTRY)\"\n235: \t@echo \"  DOCKER_TAG=$(DOCKER_TAG)\"\n236: \t@echo \"  VERSION=$(VERSION)\"\n237: \t@echo \"  COMMIT_SHA=$(COMMIT_SHA)\"\n\n(End of file - total 237 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Makefile for AgentCube Docker builds\n# Provides targets for building, pushing, and managing container images\n\n# Docker configuration\nDOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\nDOCKER_TAG ?= latest\nVERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty 2>/dev/null || echo \"dev\")\nCOMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")\n\n# Image names\nWORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\nROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router\nPICOD_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod\n\n# Build all images\n.PHONY: docker-build-all\ndocker-build-all: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-picod\n\t@echo \"✓ All images built successfully\"\n\n# Build Workload Manager image","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/Makefile","time":{"start":1775882566262,"end":1775882566277}}}}
