{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882632464,"sessionID":"ses_28526aca8fferZlun7r4EHxBjU","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad98712001UY8WqJoDQQTJGl","messageID":"msg_d7ad97ac4001RLYLeGNh06V76M","sessionID":"ses_28526aca8fferZlun7r4EHxBjU","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_4db95d650e2047889d98e5b5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/tasks.md","content":"# AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系 Tasks\n\n**Module:** root  \n**Language:** Makefile  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Docker Build Targets\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Define Docker configuration variables\n  - Add `DOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh`\n  - Add `DOCKER_TAG ?= latest`\n  - Add `VERSION` with git describe fallback\n  - Add `COMMIT_SHA` with git rev-parse fallback\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: All variables defined with correct defaults\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Define image name variables\n  - Add `WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager`\n  - Add `ROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router`\n  - Add `PICOD_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: All three image variables defined\n\n- [ ] **T1.3** Create docker-build-all aggregate target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-build-all`\n  - Set dependency on all three build targets\n  - Add success message\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make docker-build-all` builds all images\n\n- [ ] **T1.4** Create docker-build-workloadmanager target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-build-workloadmanager`\n  - Build with `-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Pass `VERSION` and `COMMIT_SHA` as build args\n  - Tag with `DOCKER_TAG`, `COMMIT_SHA`, `VERSION`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Image builds with correct tags\n\n- [ ] **T1.5** Create docker-build-router target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-build-router`\n  - Build with `-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Pass `VERSION` and `COMMIT_SHA` as build args\n  - Tag with `DOCKER_TAG`, `COMMIT_SHA`, `VERSION`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Image builds with correct tags\n\n- [ ] **T1.6** Create docker-build-picod target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-build-picod`\n  - Build with `-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Pass `VERSION` and `COMMIT_SHA` as build args\n  - Tag with `DOCKER_TAG`, `COMMIT_SHA`, `VERSION`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Image builds with correct tags\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Docker Push Targets\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create docker-push-all aggregate target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-push-all`\n  - Set dependency on all three push targets\n  - Add success message\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make docker-push-all` pushes all images\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Create docker-push-workloadmanager target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-push-workloadmanager`\n  - Push all three tags: `DOCKER_TAG`, `COMMIT_SHA`, `VERSION`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: All tags pushed to registry\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Create docker-push-router target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-push-router`\n  - Push all three tags: `DOCKER_TAG`, `COMMIT_SHA`, `VERSION`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: All tags pushed to registry\n\n- [ ] **T2.4** Create docker-push-picod target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-push-picod`\n  - Push all three tags: `DOCKER_TAG`, `COMMIT_SHA`, `VERSION`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: All tags pushed to registry\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Kind Cluster Integration Targets\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Create kind-load-all aggregate target\n  - Add `.PHONY: kind-load-all`\n  - Set dependency on all three load targets\n  - Add success message\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make kind-load-all` loads all images\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Create kind-load-workloadmanager target\n  - Add `.PHONY: kind-load-workloadmanager`\n  - Run `kind load docker-image $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Image loaded to Kind cluster\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Create kind-load-router target\n  - Add `.PHONY: kind-load-router`\n  - Run `kind load docker-image $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Image loaded to Kind cluster\n\n- [ ] **T3.4** Create kind-load-picod target\n  - Add `.PHONY: kind-load-picod`\n  - Run `kind load docker-image $(PICOD_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Image loaded to Kind cluster\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Multi-Architecture Build Targets\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Create docker-buildx-all aggregate target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-buildx-all`\n  - Set dependency on all three buildx targets\n  - Add success message\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make docker-buildx-all` builds all multi-arch images\n\n- [ ] **T4.2** Create docker-buildx-workloadmanager target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-buildx-workloadmanager`\n  - Build with `--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64`\n  - Use `-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile`\n  - Add `--push` flag\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Multi-arch image built and pushed\n\n- [ ] **T4.3** Create docker-buildx-router target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-buildx-router`\n  - Build with `--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64`\n  - Use `-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router`\n  - Add `--push` flag\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Multi-arch image built and pushed\n\n- [ ] **T4.4** Create docker-buildx-picod target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-buildx-picod`\n  - Build with `--platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64`\n  - Use `-f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n  - Add `--push` flag\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Multi-arch image built and pushed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Cleanup Target\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Create docker-clean target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-clean`\n  - Remove all three images with all tags\n  - Use `-` prefix on docker rmi commands to ignore errors\n  - Use `|| true` for graceful failure\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make docker-clean` removes images safely\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Validation Targets\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Create docker-validate aggregate target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-validate`\n  - Set dependency on all three validate targets\n  - Add success message\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make docker-validate` validates all images\n\n- [ ] **T6.2** Create docker-validate-workloadmanager target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-validate-workloadmanager`\n  - Run `./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` with image name\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Validation script executed\n\n- [ ] **T6.3** Create docker-validate-router target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-validate-router`\n  - Run `./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` with image name\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Validation script executed\n\n- [ ] **T6.4** Create docker-validate-picod target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-validate-picod`\n  - Run `./deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` with image name\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Validation script executed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Test Targets\n\n- [ ] **T7.1** Create docker-test aggregate target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-test`\n  - Set dependency on `docker-test-build` and `docker-test-runtime`\n  - Add success message\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: `make docker-test` runs all tests\n\n- [ ] **T7.2** Create docker-test-build target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-test-build`\n  - Run `./deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Build tests executed\n\n- [ ] **T7.3** Create docker-test-runtime target\n  - Add `.PHONY: docker-test-runtime`\n  - Run `./deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Runtime tests executed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Help Target\n\n- [ ] **T8.1** Create help target with build targets documentation\n  - Add `.PHONY: help`\n  - Print \"AgentCube Docker Makefile\" header\n  - Print \"Build targets:\" section with descriptions\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Help shows build targets\n\n- [ ] **T8.2** Add push targets documentation to help\n  - Print \"Push targets:\" section with descriptions\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Help shows push targets\n\n- [ ] **T8.3** Add Kind targets documentation to help\n  - Print \"Kind targets:\" section with descriptions\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Help shows Kind targets\n\n- [ ] **T8.4** Add multi-arch targets documentation to help\n  - Print \"Multi-arch targets:\" section with descriptions\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Help shows multi-arch targets\n\n- [ ] **T8.5** Add test & validate targets documentation to help\n  - Print \"Test & validate targets:\" section with descriptions\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Help shows test and validate targets\n\n- [ ] **T8.6** Add variables documentation to help\n  - Print \"Variables:\" section with current values\n  - Show `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `VERSION`, `COMMIT_SHA`\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Help shows variable values\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Makefile Structure & Best Practices\n\n- [ ] **T9.1** Ensure all targets are declared as .PHONY\n  - Add `.PHONY` declaration for all 20+ targets\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: No target conflicts with files\n\n- [ ] **T9.2** Use consistent indentation with tabs\n  - All recipe lines use tab characters (not spaces)\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Makefile parses correctly\n\n- [ ] **T9.3** Add echo messages for user feedback\n  - Each target prints progress/success messages\n  - Use `@echo` for silent execution with output\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: User sees clear progress during execution\n\n- [ ] **T9.4** Use variable references consistently\n  - Reference images via `$(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE)` not hardcoded\n  - Reference tags via `$(DOCKER_TAG)` not hardcoded\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: All image/tag references use variables\n\n- [ ] **T9.5** Organize targets in logical order\n  - Group: Variables → Build → Push → Kind → Buildx → Clean → Validate → Test → Help\n  - File: `Makefile`\n  - Verify: Related targets are adjacent\n\n---\n\n## Phase 10: Make Target Testing\n\n- [ ] **T10.1** Test docker-build-all target\n  - Command: `make docker-build-all`\n  - Verify: All three images build successfully\n  - Verify: Images tagged with `latest`\n\n- [ ] **T10.2** Test with custom DOCKER_TAG\n  - Command: `make docker-build-all DOCKER_TAG=v1.0.0`\n  - Verify: Images tagged with `v1.0.0`\n\n- [ ] **T10.3** Test with custom VERSION\n  - Command: `make docker-build-all VERSION=2.0.0`\n  - Verify: Images tagged with `2.0.0`\n\n- [ ] **T10.4** Test docker-clean target\n  - Command: `make docker-clean`\n  - Verify: Images removed (errors ignored if not present)\n\n- [ ] **T10.5** Test help target\n  - Command: `make help`\n  - Verify: All targets documented with correct descriptions\n  - Verify: Variable values displayed\n\n- [ ] **T10.6** Test individual build targets\n  - Command: `make docker-build-workloadmanager`\n  - Command: `make docker-build-router`\n  - Command: `make docker-build-picod`\n  - Verify: Each builds independently\n\n- [ ] **T10.7** Test individual push targets (dry-run or skip if no registry)\n  - Verify: Push targets have correct image references\n  - Verify: Push targets use all three tags\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. ✅ `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `VERSION`, `COMMIT_SHA` variables defined\n2. ✅ Image name variables for all three components defined\n3. ✅ `docker-build-all` builds all three images sequentially\n4. ✅ Individual build targets for each component exist\n5. ✅ All build targets tag images with DOCKER_TAG, COMMIT_SHA, VERSION\n6. ✅ `docker-push-all` pushes all images to registry\n7. ✅ Individual push targets push all three tags\n8. ✅ `kind-load-all` loads all images to Kind cluster\n9. ✅ Individual kind-load targets exist for each component\n10. ✅ `docker-buildx-all` builds multi-arch images (amd64, arm64)\n11. ✅ Multi-arch build targets use `--push` flag\n12. ✅ `docker-clean` safely removes local images\n13. ✅ `docker-validate` validates all images\n14. ✅ `docker-test` runs build and runtime tests\n15. ✅ `make help` displays all targets with descriptions\n16. ✅ Help shows